{"tid":621281,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"「魚缸」如果底吹 駁左濾筒仲洗唔洗人手吸魚屎","createTime":"2018-04-08T07:49:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T17:52:06.000Z","uid":59090,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"527d206bc3e5c6371a251c5a7c3a5105782081ec","tid":621281,"uid":59090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T07:49:54.000Z","msg":"如題，新手想開新缸，養少量魚同蝦，如果底吹(係浪板入面將水流由底向上沖過底材既砂石層，令魚屎唔會係底材積累)，<br />\n咁樣過濾既淨化水質效果足夠嗎？<br />\n<br />\n會唔會沖晒d屎出黎分解唔切？<br />\n<br />\n仲需唔需要人手吸魚屎？"},{"pid":"b412609c1f46097ab5613549b75906b55487bd39","tid":621281,"uid":181129,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T08:13:31.000Z","msg":"底吹通常都有好多死位藏屎"},{"pid":"dd4cf466184dd0ba6660f428a144080769e4e324","tid":621281,"uid":59090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b412609c1f46097ab5613549b75906b55487bd39","tid":621281,"uid":181129,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T08:13:31.000Z","msg":"底吹通常都有好多死位藏屎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T08:16:35.000Z","msg":"底濾係咪會好 d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1187990f67e79469ec191692fe9ec9f03c4e6487","tid":621281,"uid":181129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T08:29:26.000Z","msg":"有濾桶其實可以唔用底沙，用厚底沙又等同第二個濾桶。"},{"pid":"0665aad77625f068b04c20e402bc2a0abf03d2d5","tid":621281,"uid":55016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T08:45:12.000Z","msg":"其實唔洗點理，整好個生化系統就得（用開泥）"},{"pid":"f0e40cfc7f10e6f5481affe49a4d72ed46a0c311","tid":621281,"uid":55542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T09:00:20.000Z","msg":"圖呢？？"},{"pid":"5624d99b3ae9264b24f844ebec03300967f3c040","tid":621281,"uid":44171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T09:05:24.000Z","msg":"邊種都OK啦, 反正半年後又想換晒D草, 清晒D泥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15ae9fcc7ce5720dff9dea8b6ab953bfcf25b539","tid":621281,"uid":14